Second sales record for Honda
In November, Honda will launch the second generation of Jazz.
True, its predecessor had a large enough passenger compartment, but the design of the interior of the new model is even more spacious.
This is coupled with sophisticated mechanics that make driving more comfortable and increase fuel savings.
