The larger interior is guaranteed by the new body on the one hand and the fuel tank in the middle on the other - this solution is already known from the previous Jazz.
In addition, the total cargo space of the so-called double floor luggage compartment has increased, currently exceeding the capacity of the first generation by 399 litres, i.e. 19 litres.
